Diamond::

She tried as hard as she could, but the loss of mech fluid made her 
drowzy.  She closed her eyes and had to use her heat sensors to 
detect anything that moved around her.  She felt her scales burn and 
hurt from that lighening.  She hissed and stayed curled up near the 
doorway to the cargo bay.  She would put up her last fight here.
